{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But unluckily there were two of them-- because they came maybe two dozens of these soldiers-- two of them were, were sent to our house, to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't tell us if one night or two nights, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they came and they had to sleep somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I moved to a little-- you know, a peasant house has one bedroom, one kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sleeping normally on the kitchen floor, because there it's hot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the two soldiers were sleeping in because the woman with children-- she had two children-- she was in the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was sleeping in a, in a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is a little room where they have potatoes and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't complain, I was happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was only worried what the Germans will-- I didn't talk to them, because I couldn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they, they were, they were Austrians, in the age of 50 or 60.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were old Austrians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were used for this sort of work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were really looking for partisans or for the uprising, the people who were in the middle of the uprising.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but the front came, luckily, so close to our village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we heard already the couple of nights bombardment, day and night, and even, in the evening, flashes of the shots.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And suddenly, one early in the morning, we were occupied by the retreating German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were still very organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had the tanks in the outskirts, not in the streets of the village, because it was too small.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were all around the area, because they were retreating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Russians, they drove them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was worried that the change over can be very tragical.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
